  "shape_1_per_frame": "xs = xs*(1 - 2*above(xm,0.99) - 2*below(xm,0.01));\nys = ys*(1 - 2*above(ym,0.99) - 2*below(ym,0.01));\n\nxm = xm + 0.03*xs*(sin(time*0.53)*0.6 + 0.4*cos(time*0.62));\nym = ym + 0.03*ys*(sin(time*0.2942)*0.6 + 0.29*cos(time*0.68));\n\nx = xm;\ny = ym;\n\nr = 0.5 + 0.25*sin(x*12) + 0.25*sin(y*3);\ng = 0.5 + 0.25*sin(x*7) + 0.25*sin(y*32);\nb = 0.5 + 0.25*sin(x*21) + 0.25*sin(y*16);\nr2 = r; g2 = g; b2 = b;\nrad = 0.2*(bass_att + mid_att + treb_att)/3;",
