  "shape_2_per_frame": "xs = xs*(1 - 2*above(xm,0.99) - 2*below(xm,0.01));\nys = ys*(1 - 2*above(ym,0.99) - 2*below(ym,0.01));\n\nxm = xm + 0.03*xs*(sin(time*0.35)*0.5 + 0.5*cos(time*0.87));\nym = ym + 0.03*ys*(sin(time*0.92)*0.3 + 0.7*cos(time*0.26));\n\nx = xm;\ny = ym;\n\nr = 0.5 + 0.5*sin(time*0.25);\ng = 0.5 + abs(r)*sin(time*0.5);\nb = 0.5 + abs(g)*sin(time);\nr2 = r; g2 = g; b2 = b;\nrad = 1.6*(bass_att + mid_att + treb_att)/3;"
